l__channel-list","popover":{"title":"Unread, Mute & Channel Settings","description":"Each row shows an unread badge, and the header icon shows your total; opening a conversation marks it read. Mute a noisy channel from its row to silence notifications without leaving. Open Channel settings (the gear) to rename or edit a channel or leave it — members are Member, Admin, or Owner.","side":"right"}}]}"""
